0.6:

- contexts can be moved around (javascript required)
- hidden fields aren't fetched from sql server anymore
- added a tooltip for hidden fields
- all interaction links are forms now
- list elements are sorted now
- several contexts can be displayed on the same page

0.5: 

- implemented a more consequent MVC pattern.
- id field isn't visible in the editor anymore.

